1. *Trenutku* je prošlo. (In a moment it was gone.)
2. U tom *trenutku* je shvatio. (At that moment he realized.)
3. Ona je uživala u *trenutku*. (She enjoyed the moment.)
4. U tom *trenutku* se sve promenilo. (At that moment everything changed.)
5. *Trenutku* je bilo sve gotovo. (In a moment it was all over.)